cu.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum value 'bad' will cause parsing errors in ASN.1 messages and prevent proper protocol handling.

du.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum value 'bad' will cause parsing errors in ASN.1 messages and prevent proper protocol handling.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知的枚舉值 'bad' 會導致 ASN.1 訊息解析錯誤，並阻止正確的協議處理。
